    public class ChannelCatalogTesting
extends java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,SignageContent>
implements ChannelCatalog
    Holds the definitions of some Channels in the XOC signage system so that a channel can be selected in the touch panel. This was a prototype that was used before the database was established.
